---
import Paragraph from "../ui/Paragraph";
import SmallTitle from "../ui/SmallTitle";
---

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20">
  <!-- First feature card -->
  <div
    class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 group relative overflow-hidden"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute -top-8 -right-8 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-400 to-teal-300 rounded-full opacity-20 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-500"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-6">
      <div class="p-3 bg-teal-100 rounded-lg">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-6 w-6 text-teal-600"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <SmallTitle className="mb-0">Création intelligente</SmallTitle>
    </div>

    <Paragraph>
      Un simple prompt suffit pour générer des collections complètes de
      flashcards pertinentes. Combinez texte et sources externes pour des
      résultats encore plus riches.
    </Paragraph>

    <div class="my-6 p-5 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-100">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
        <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-400 mr-1.5"></span>
        <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 mr-1.5"></span>
        <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-400 mr-1.5"></span>
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 ml-2">Exemple de prompt</span>
      </div>
      <Paragraph className="text-sm italic">
        "Crée-moi des flashcards sur les planètes du système solaire + <span
          class="text-teal-600 font-medium"
          >importe mon PDF sur l'astronomie</span
        >"
      </Paragraph>
    </div>

    <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-600">
      <li class="flex items-center">
        <svg
          class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-teal-500"
          fill="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
        >
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
        <Paragraph> Générez des collections complètes en secondes </Paragraph>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center">
        <svg
          class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-teal-500"
          fill="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
        >
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
        <Paragraph> Ajoutez du contenu à vos collections existantes </Paragraph>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center">
        <svg
          class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-teal-500"
          fill="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
        >
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
        <Paragraph>
          Combinez prompt et sources pour plus de précision
        </Paragraph>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Second feature card -->
  <div
    class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 group relative overflow-hidden"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute -top-8 -right-8 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-blue-300 rounded-full opacity-20 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-500"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-6">
      <div class="p-3 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-8l-4-4m0 0L8 8m4-4v12"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <SmallTitle className="mb-0"> Import multi-source universel </SmallTitle>
    </div>

    <Paragraph>
      Convertissez instantanément n'importe quel contenu en flashcards. Notre
      système extrait l'essentiel de vos documents, médias ou pages web.
    </Paragraph>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-3 my-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <div
          class="h-12 w-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg mb-2"
          style="background-color: #FF0000;"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-6 w-6 text-white"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z"
            ></path>
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-600">Vidéos</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <div
          class="h-12 w-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg mb-2"
          style="background-color: #DB4437;"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-6 w-6 text-white"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-600">Documents</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <div
          class="h-12 w-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg mb-2"
          style="background-color: #4285F4;"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-6 w-6 text-white"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-600">Sites web</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <div
          class="h-12 w-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg mb-2"
          style="background-color: #0F9D58;"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-6 w-6 text-white"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-600">Apps externes</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-600">
      <li class="flex items-center">
        <svg
          class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-blue-500"
          fill="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
        >
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
        YouTube, PDF, Excel, Word, Pages, slides, etc.
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center">
        <svg
          class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-blue-500"
          fill="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
        >
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
        Importez vos collections Anki, Quizlet existantes
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center">
        <svg
          class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-blue-500"
          fill="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
        >
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
        Ajoutez du texte simple ou du contenu copié-collé
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
